      "description": "Flow rate: 3.0–7.0 L/min (±0.05 L/min measurement uncertainty). Pump rotational speed: 2400–3600 RPM (±10 RPM). Inlet pressure: 5–15 mmHg. Outlet pressure: 80–120 mmHg. Fluid temperature: 37 ± 0.5 °C. Hematocrit: 35–45%. All five experimental operating points used for validation fall within these bounds."
    }
  },
